  "body": "Bin-Bin Zhang (UAH) reports on behalf of the Fermi GBM team:\n\n\n\n\"The Fermi Gamma-ray Burst Monitor (GBM) trigger 451588780/150424722\n\nat 17:19:37.07 UT on the 24th of April 2015, tentatively classified\nas a GRB, is in fact not due to a GRB. This trigger is due to local particles.���\n\n\n\n���\nSent from Mailbox"
